1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper focuses on computer vision tasks such as saliency detection and object proposal generation, which are important topics in the field of computer vision. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed method for object discovery can be considered as an AI technique, as it involves utilizing eigenvectors of the affinity matrix to discover objects in an image. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper involves formulating a new affinity matrix and cohesion measurement for object regions, which can be seen as a machine learning task. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The proposed method can also be applied to image retrieval tasks, as it can help in discovering objects in an image that can be used for retrieval purposes. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with image processing and analysis, which is a key aspect of multimedia research.
